title: Worst Date Wednesday: "The Singer"
description: Amorette tells us the story about a guy she met in college who would walk around the halls singing.  He asked her to a group friend drive-in but when she gets there, she's the only one that "showed up".  The date ends with a lack of pants and a doorway.
